Thu Jun 18 00:00:00 UTC 2015 - mschnitzer@suse.de

Stable release DocManager 3.0.0:

* Bugfixes:
  - Fixed #54 (usage output irritating)
  - Fixed #53 (Default property for product or release is missing)
  - Fixed #52 (Inconsistent reporting)
  - Fixed #51 (Include filename in error messages)
  - Fixed #50 (Proceed on error when handling multiple files)
  - Fixed #48 (docmanager set --priority 1,2 xml/FILE.xml causes traceback)

* New features:
  - Added xml and table output format
  - Option `--repository` is a new option in init and set (have a look into
    the man page)

* Miscellaneous:
  - Performance improvemenets
  - Internal code improvement
  - Updated man page and restructured some things
  - Fixed some typos
